    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Motor-driven machines, such as endless belts or a series of rollers, used for the continuous transport of material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
